---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Leblanc Estate Law Grew Professional Referrals 3.9x | Lead Flow North" description="An Ottawa estate planning firm built a systematic referral network with financial advisors and accountants.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/legal-services/estate-planning" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Estate Planning Law
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Leblanc Estate Law Grew Professional Referrals 3.9x
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          An Ottawa estate planning firm built a systematic referral network with financial advisors and accountants.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-green-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">71%</div>
              <div class="text-emerald-100">Consultation Booking</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">3.9x</div>
              <div class="text-emerald-100">Professional Referrals</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">67%</div>
              <div class="text-emerald-100">Plan Update Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">$72K</div>
              <div class="text-emerald-100">Monthly Revenue</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Firm:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Leblanc Estate Law</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Ottawa, ON</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Practice:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Estate planning</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Focus:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Wills, trusts, powers of attorney</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Michelle Leblanc relied on sporadic referrals from financial advisors. Lead follow-up was inconsistent—people would inquire about wills and then procrastinate for months. Past clients rarely updated their plans even after major life changes.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented systematic financial advisor nurturing with valuable content, persistent lead follow-up for procrastinators, educational sequences about estate planning concepts, and annual review reminders for existing clients.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Consultation booking rate hit 71%. Professional referrals increased 3.9x. 67% of clients now update their plans regularly. Monthly revenue grew to $72K. Financial advisors now call Michelle first when clients need estate planning.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-emerald-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "Financial advisors used to refer occasionally. Now they have a system—when a client needs estate planning, they think of me automatically. That's the power of staying top-of-mind."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">— Michelle Leblanc, Founder</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-green-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Build Your Referral Network?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
